## Complete Blue Nile Three-Stone Catalog

### Marquise Side Stone — The Most Reviewed Diamond Three-Stone

Marquise-cut side stones flank the center diamond, creating a pointed, elongated wing profile on either side. The V-tip of the marquise points away from the center, widening the apparent face-up size of the ring significantly. 152 reviews across all three metals makes this the most-purchased all-diamond three-stone series on Blue Nile.

[![Blue Nile Marquise Cut Diamond Three Stone Ring White Gold](/images/bn-3stone-502489-rnd-wg.avif)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/marquise-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-315103?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)

**[Marquise Cut Diamond Three Stone in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/marquise-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-315103?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $1,970 · 152 reviews · Item #315103**
The most-reviewed all-diamond three-stone setting in Blue Nile's catalog. White gold is the classic choice for marquise side stones — the colorless metal emphasizes the angular wing shape of the marquise cut. G or better color for the center stone; the marquise side stones will reflect the metal tone into the center stone from the side. Setting includes the two marquise side diamonds.

**[Marquise Cut Diamond Three Stone in 14K Yellow Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/marquise-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-by-james-allen-item-315107?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $1,970 · 152 reviews · Item #315107**
Same 152-review purchase signal in yellow gold. The warm metal gives the marquise wings a vintage warmth that white gold cannot produce. H color minimum for the center stone. Particularly effective for yellow diamonds or near-colorless centers where the warm metal counterbalances body color.

**[Marquise Cut Diamond Three Stone in 14K Rose Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/marquise-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-by-james-allen-item-315100?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $1,970 · 152 reviews · Item #315100**
Rose gold marquise three-stone — the most photographed of the three colorways. The pink metal against the pointed wing silhouette is visually distinctive. G–H center color; the rose gold prongs warm near-colorless centers slightly.

