### Scroll Undergallery Three Stone — 74 Reviews

[![Blue Nile Three Stone Scroll Undergallery Rose Gold](/images/bn-3stone-501490-rnd-rg.avif)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-with-scroll-undergallery-in-14k-rose-gold-by-james-allen-item-315021?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)

The Scroll Undergallery design features decorative scroll metalwork visible below the setting — the undergallery (the underside of the ring band) has ornate curved metalwork instead of a plain flat gallery. This adds vintage detail without changing the face-up appearance.

**[Three Stone With Scroll Undergallery in 14K Rose Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-with-scroll-undergallery-in-14k-rose-gold-by-james-allen-item-315021?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,410 · 74 reviews · Item #315021**
The scroll design in rose gold is the standout colorway — 74 reviews in rose gold alone. The pink metal paired with ornate undergallery scrollwork creates the strongest vintage-romantic aesthetic in the three-stone catalog. G–H center stone for rose gold.

**[Three Stone With Scroll Undergallery in 14K Yellow Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-with-scroll-undergallery-in-14k-yellow-gold-by-james-allen-item-315025?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,410 · 74 reviews · Item #315025**
Yellow gold Scroll Undergallery. The warm metal amplifies the vintage character of the scroll work. H minimum center stone. Strong choice for buyers who want a heirloom aesthetic without crossing into designer pricing.

**[Three Stone With Scroll Undergallery in Platinum](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-with-scroll-undergallery-in-platinum-by-james-allen-item-315020?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,620 · 74 reviews · Item #315020**
Platinum scroll undergallery — $210 more than the rose gold version. For D–G color centers. The platinum scroll metalwork has a cooler, more refined finish than 14k and holds detail better long-term.

