### Blue Sapphire Three Stone — Highest-Reviewed Gemstone Setting

**[Classic Pear Shaped Sapphire Engagement Ring in Platinum](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/classic-pear-shaped-sapphire-engagement-ring-in-platinum-item-194499?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,610 · 207 reviews · Item #194499**
207 reviews makes this the most-reviewed setting in the entire three-stone catalog — and it includes two pear-shaped blue sapphire side stones. You are paying $2,610 for the platinum setting and two genuine blue sapphires. At sapphire retail, this is exceptional value. The pear sapphire points flank the center diamond in an iconic royal-inspired design — the same configuration made famous by Princess Diana's engagement ring (now Kate Middleton's). D–G center stone; the blue sapphire side stones contrast strongly against colorless diamonds.

**[Round Blue Sapphire Three Stone in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/round-blue-sapphire-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-310976?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,000 · 25 reviews · Item #310976**
Round sapphire side stones in white gold. The round blue sapphire design is more subdued than the pear-point version — the stones sit level with the center rather than pointing away, creating a compact three-stone cluster. 25 reviews across all three metal colorways indicates steady purchase volume.

**[Round Blue Sapphire Three Stone in 14K Yellow Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/round-blue-sapphire-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-by-james-allen-item-310979?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,000 · 25 reviews · Item #310979**
Yellow gold round sapphire. The combination of blue sapphire side stones and yellow gold creates a distinctly vintage royal aesthetic — the closest catalog equivalent to historical royal jewelry pieces.

**[Round Blue Sapphire Three Stone in 14K Rose Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/round-blue-sapphire-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-by-james-allen-item-310975?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,000 · 25 reviews · Item #310975**
Rose gold round sapphire — the most unconventional colorway. The blue-pink-blue color story (sapphire-rose gold-sapphire) is distinctive and reads as modern rather than traditional.

**[Round Blue Sapphire Three Stone in Platinum](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/round-blue-sapphire-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-platinum-by-james-allen-item-310974?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,550 · 25 reviews · Item #310974**
Platinum round sapphire. The $550 premium over 14k for platinum is meaningful — the colorless metal creates the strongest contrast with the blue sapphire side stones and is the correct structural choice for long-term wear.

