### Baguette Side Stone Three Stone

Baguette side stones create a clean, Art Deco aesthetic with the rectangular step-cut flanking the center stone. This is the most architectural three-stone configuration.

[![Blue Nile Tapered Baguette Three Stone Yellow Gold](/images/bn-3stone-tapered-baguette-yg.avif)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/tapered-baguette-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-1-6-ct-tw-item-192870?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)

**[Tapered Baguette Diamond Engagement Ring in 14K Yellow Gold (1/6 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/tapered-baguette-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-1-6-ct-tw-item-192870?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $1,910 · 19 reviews · Item #192870**
Tapered baguette side stones — the baguette narrows at the end closest to the center stone, creating a graduated, wedge-shaped flanking stone. 1/6ct total weight. 19 reviews at the entry price point confirms this is a consistent seller. For buyers who want the baguette silhouette at the lowest available price.

**[Bezel Straight Baguette Three Stone in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-straight-baguette-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-316318?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,720 · 2 reviews · Item #316318**
Bezel-set straight baguettes — the baguette is enclosed in a metal bezel rather than set with prongs. The bezel protects the baguette's corners (which are prone to chipping in prong settings) and creates a more modern, streamlined look. White gold bezel with rectangular baguettes is a clean, architectural design.

**[Bezel Straight Baguette Three Stone in 14K Yellow Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-straight-baguette-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-by-james-allen-item-316319?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,720 · Item #316319**
Yellow gold bezel baguette. The warm metal with bezel-set rectangles creates a strong Art Deco statement. H minimum center stone.

**[Bezel Straight Baguette Three Stone in Platinum](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-straight-baguette-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-platinum-by-james-allen-item-316317?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,890 · 2 reviews · Item #316317**
Platinum bezel baguette — $170 more than the 14k versions. The platinum bezel setting is the most durable way to set a baguette diamond and the correct choice for daily wear.

**[Three-Stone Tapered Baguette in 14K White Gold (1/4 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/three-stone-tapered-baguette-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-4-ct-tw-item-203640?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $3,410 · 3 reviews · Item #203640**
1/4ct total weight in the two tapered baguette side stones in white gold — more substantial than the 1/6ct entry version.

**[Three-Stone Tapered Baguette in Platinum (5/8 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/three-stone-tapered-baguette-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-5-8-ct-tw-item-191941?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $7,630 · 1 review · Item #191941**
5/8ct total weight in tapered baguette side stones in platinum — the highest-weight baguette option. At $7,630, the setting price includes meaningful baguette diamond weight and platinum construction.

