### Pear Side Stone Three Stone

**[Pear Sidestone Diamond Engagement Ring in 14K Yellow Gold (1/4 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/pear-sidestone-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-1-4-ct-tw-item-192877?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $1,820 · 63 reviews · Item #192877**
63 reviews on a pear side-stone setting at $1,820 is a strong signal. Two pear-cut side stones flank the center diamond with their pointed tips directed away from center — creating a balanced, symmetrical layout where each pear's outline echoes the other. Yellow gold is the only metal available for this specific design; the warm metal suits the organic pear silhouette.

