### East-West & Specialty Side Stone

**[East-West Sidestone and Pavé in 14K White Gold (1/4 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/east-west-sidestone-and-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-4-ct-tw-item-192396?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $1,840 · 19 reviews · Item #192396**
The side stones are positioned east-west (horizontally) rather than at the standard 3 and 9 o'clock alignment. This rotates the visual axis and creates a wider, lower-profile face-up appearance. The horizontal orientation suits oval and marquise center stones where the stone itself reads east-west. Includes 1/4ct total side stones plus pavé on the shank.

**[East-West Sidestone and Pavé in 14K Rose Gold (1/4 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/east-west-sidestone-and-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-1-4-ct-tw-item-192397?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $1,840 · 19 reviews · Item #192397**
Rose gold east-west. The horizontal stone orientation in rose gold reads as distinctly modern and fashion-forward — a strong choice for oval center buyers who want their setting to match the stone's elongated character.

**[Lace Bridge Three Stone and Pavé in 14K Yellow Gold (1/2 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/lace-bridge-three-stone-and-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-1-2-ct-tw-item-197213?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,645 · 10 reviews · Item #197213**
Lace-style metalwork bridges connect the side stones to the center — a structurally unique design where the joining elements are decorative. 1/2ct total weight. 10 reviews confirms intentional purchases. Yellow gold with lace metalwork creates an ornate, vintage feel.

[![Blue Nile Lace Bridge Three Stone Round Diamond Ring](/images/bn-3stone-lace-bridge-round.avif)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/lace-bridge-three-stone-and-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-1-2-ct-tw-item-197213?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)

[![Blue Nile Lace Bridge Three Stone Ring Detail 2](/images/bn-3stone-lace-bridge-round-2.avif)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/lace-bridge-three-stone-and-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-1-2-ct-tw-item-197213?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)

[![Blue Nile Lace Bridge Three Stone Ring Detail 3](/images/bn-3stone-lace-bridge-round-3.avif)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/lace-bridge-three-stone-and-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-1-2-ct-tw-item-197213?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)

**[Three-Stone Trillion Diamond Engagement Ring in Platinum (1/3 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/three-stone-trillion-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-1-3-ct-tw-item-192950?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $3,590 · 4 reviews · Item #192950**
Trillion (triangular) side stones flanking the center — the three-pointed triangular cuts create a starburst-like side profile. 1/3ct total weight in the two trilliants. Platinum is the only metal offered. A genuinely distinctive silhouette — the trillion creates visible pointed shadow plays at the stone-to-stone interface.

**[Three-Stone Elongated Princess in 14K White Gold (1/2 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/three-stone-elongated-princess-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-2-ct-tw-item-203668?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $4,450 · Item #203668**
Elongated rectangular princess-cut side stones — similar to baguettes but with the sparkle pattern of a princess cut. 1/2ct total weight. White gold.

**[Three-Stone Half-Moon Sidestone in 14K White Gold (1/2 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/three-stone-half-moon-sidestone-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-2-ct-tw-item-203679?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $5,320 · Item #203679**
Half-moon (D-shaped) side stones — the flat edge of each side stone faces the center diamond, creating a crescent silhouette on each side. The half-moon shape creates a "hug" effect around the center stone's girdle. 1/2ct total weight. White gold only.

**[Three-Stone Trapezoid Sidestone in 14K Rose Gold (1/2 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/three-stone-trapezoid-sidestone-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-1-2-ct-tw-item-203681?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $5,900 · Item #203681**
Trapezoid (step-cut with angled sides) side stones in rose gold. 1/2ct total weight. The trapezoid side stone's angled outer edge creates a graduated visual transition from the center outward.

**[Three-Stone Trapezoid Sidestone in Platinum (1/2 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/three-stone-trapezoid-sidestone-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-1-2-ct-tw-item-192941?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $6,890 · Item #192941**
Platinum trapezoid side stone three-stone. The step-cut trapezoid in platinum is the most architecturally refined three-stone configuration in the mid-range catalog.

**[Pavé Knife Edge Diamond Three Stone in 14K Yellow Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/pave-knife-edge-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-by-james-allen-item-315259?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $3,400 · 9 reviews · Item #315259**
Three-stone layout with a knife-edge shank — the band tapers to a thin ridge, creating light play along the shank independently of the three stones. 9 reviews confirms purchase intent at this price point.

**[Pavé Knife Edge Diamond Three Stone in 14K Rose Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/pave-knife-edge-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-by-james-allen-item-315260?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $3,400 · 9 reviews · Item #315260**
Rose gold knife-edge three-stone. The pink metal along the knife-edge ridge catches light differently than white gold — a warmer, more dimensional sparkle along the band.

