The lowest-priced setting in the entire three-stone catalog — $1,680 for a petite lab-grown three-stone in rose gold. 20 reviews confirms steady purchase volume. For buyers who want three-stone symbolism at the absolute minimum setting investment. The lab-grown side stones are chemically identical to mined diamonds — the only difference is origin.

**[Wrapped Shank Three Stone Lab-Grown Diamond in 14K Yellow Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/wrapped-shank-three-stone-lab-grown-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-item-309400?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $1,870 · 4 reviews · Item #309400**
Wrapped shank three-stone — the band wraps or interweaves at the shoulder near the setting. Lab-grown side stones in yellow gold. A more distinctive design than the petite trio at only $190 more.

**[Classic Pear Shaped Lab-Grown Diamond Engagement Ring in 14K White Gold (1/2 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/classic-pear-shaped-lab-grown-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-2-ct-tw-item-296444?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,520 · 40 reviews · Item #296444**
Pear-shaped lab-grown side stones in white gold — 1/2ct total weight, 40 reviews. The highest-reviewed lab-grown three-stone design in the catalog. The pear lab-grown side stones at 1/2ct total provide substantial apparent size for a lab-grown price point. 40 reviews is a strong signal.

**[Three-Stone Emerald Cut Lab-Grown Diamond in 14K Yellow Gold (5/8 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/three-stone-emerald-cut-lab-grown-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-5-8-ct-tw-item-309386?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,440 · 4 reviews · Item #309386**
5/8ct emerald-cut lab-grown side stones in yellow gold. Substantial step-cut diamond weight at a lab-grown price. The yellow gold and emerald cut combination creates a strong Art Deco aesthetic.

**[Three-Stone Emerald Cut Lab-Grown Diamond in Platinum (5/8 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/three-stone-emerald-cut-lab-grown-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-5-8-ct-tw-item-309394?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,695 · 4 reviews · Item #309394**
Platinum version of the emerald-cut lab-grown three-stone. For D–F centers where colorless metal is important throughout the setting.

