[![Blue Nile Gallery Collection Emerald Three Stone Halo Rose Gold](/images/bn-3stone-past-present-future.avif)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/the-gallery-collection-emerald-three-stone-halo-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-150-ct-tw-item-203787?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)

**[Gallery Collection™ Emerald Three Stone Halo in 14K Rose Gold (1.50 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/the-gallery-collection-emerald-three-stone-halo-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-rose-gold-150-ct-tw-item-203787?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $13,405 · Item #203787**
1.50ct total weight in the setting alone — emerald-cut three-stone with halo, all in rose gold. At $13,405, the side stone and accent diamond weight is substantial. The setting price includes 1.50ct of diamonds; your total ring cost with a center stone will be $20,000+.

**[Gallery Collection™ Emerald Three Stone Halo in Platinum](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/the-gallery-collection-emerald-three-stone-halo-diamond-engagement-ring-in-platinum-item-194601?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $14,830 · Item #194601**
