The highest-priced engagement ring setting in Blue Nile's catalog — $24,800 for the setting alone. The Gallery Collection vintage trapezoid includes a significant total diamond weight in the side and accent positions. Yellow gold only. For buyers who consider the setting as much of an investment as the center stone.

