## Farzana's Picks by Buyer Type

**Best overall three-stone:** [Classic Pear Shaped Sapphire in Platinum](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/classic-pear-shaped-sapphire-engagement-ring-in-platinum-item-194499?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,610 · 207 reviews. The most-reviewed setting in the entire three-stone catalog. The price includes two pear sapphires. No other setting in this price range offers this much included stone value with this review depth.

**Best all-diamond three-stone:** [Marquise Cut Three Stone in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/marquise-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-315103?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $1,970 · 152 reviews. The most-reviewed all-diamond three-stone. The marquise wings maximize face-up size at the lowest price point.

**Best vintage look:** [Three Stone With Scroll Undergallery in 14K Rose Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-with-scroll-undergallery-in-14k-rose-gold-by-james-allen-item-315021?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,410 · 74 reviews. 74 reviews is strong for a decorative undergallery design. The scroll work in rose gold is the most heirloom-feeling setting at a catalog price.

**Best for lab-grown budget:** [Classic Pear Shaped Lab-Grown in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/classic-pear-shaped-lab-grown-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-2-ct-tw-item-296444?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $2,520 · 40 reviews. The highest-reviewed lab-grown three-stone. Pear side stones at 1/2ct total — significant face-up size for a lab price point.

**Best for Art Deco buyers:** [Emerald Cut Three Stone with Pavé in Platinum](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/emerald-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-with-pave-set-diamonds-in-platinum-by-james-allen-item-304297?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $3,700 · 39 reviews. Step-cut side stones in platinum. The most architectural three-stone design in the catalog.

